item.title: About
item.dc:creator: rajputanmol22749
item.content:encoded:
A highly skilled software engineer with over 2 years of professional experience in the field of technology. My passion for coding and problem-solving has led me to work with a diverse set of technologies, including .NET Core, Angular, WordPress, and more.
 

Key Highlights:

Expertise: I have a strong foundation in .NET development, allowing me to create robust and efficient web applications. My experience with Angular has allowed me to build dynamic and responsive user interfaces that enhance user experiences.
WordPress: I excel in custom WordPress development, enabling clients to have unique and functional websites tailored to their specific needs. My expertise includes theme customization, plugin development, and optimizing site performance.
Problem Solver: I thrive on challenges and love solving complex problems. Whether it's optimizing code for better performance, troubleshooting issues, or finding innovative solutions, I'm always up for the task.
Team Player: A collaborative team player who enjoys working with cross-functional teams to achieve project goals. My communication skills and ability to adapt to various team dynamics make me an asset in any development environment.
Continuous Learner: The tech industry is constantly evolving, and I am committed to staying up-to-date with the latest trends and technologies. I regularly engage in professional development to ensure that I bring the best solutions to the table.

Portfolio Highlights:

Project 1: .NET Core Web Application: Developed a scalable .NET Core web application that streamlined internal processes, resulting in a 30% increase in efficiency.
Project 2: Angular Dashboard: Designed and implemented a dynamic Angular dashboard that provided real-time analytics, enhancing data-driven decision-making.
Project 3: Custom WordPress Site: Created a custom WordPress site for a client in the e-commerce industry, resulting in a 20% increase in online sales within the first quarter.
 
I am passionate about crafting software solutions that not only meet but exceed client expectations. My dedication to quality, attention to detail, and commitment to staying at the forefront of technology make me a valuable asset to any project.
If you're interested in collaborating or learning more about my work, feel free to contact me. I'm excited to explore new opportunities and contribute to innovative projects in the world of technology.

item.title: Projects Details
item.dc:creator: rajputanmol22749
item.content:encoded:
Compro

The SaaS product for Commission Management is a cloud-based software that simplifies the commission process between salespersons and accountants. It enables salespersons to create invoices and select applicable product categories, while allowing admins to set and modify commission rules. Invoices go through an approval process, after which commissions are calculated and added to salespersons'accounts. Accountants can process payouts based on earned commissions. The product includes a userfriendly dashboard, generates reports on commission earnings, and offers features like user management, invoice tracking, and commission rule setting.

Technology Stack : PostgreSQL, MySQL, .Net Core-7 Web API, Angular 16.

Application Tracking System (ATS)

The Applicant Tracking System (ATS) is a powerful software application designed to enhance companies' hiring processes by streamlining and automating time-consuming administrative tasks. By leveraging the capabilities of the ATS, hiring managers and recruiters can effectively attract, source, interview, and evaluate candidates in a more efficient and expedient manner. The ATS acts as a centralized platform, enabling seamless organization and structure throughout the hiring journey, ultimately leading to faste and more successful recruitment outcomes.

Technology Stack : PostgreSQL, HTML, SCSS, Angular15, .Net Core-6 , BootStrap.

ProweIntra

Developed a comprehensive web application using .NET Core to streamline various operations such assalary calculation, worksheet tracking, attendance monitoring, billing, project management, leavemanagement and task assignment. Implemented efficient database management techniques to ensuredata accuracy and improved overall productivity.

Technology Stack : MySQL Database, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, AJAX, .Net Core, BootStrap.

Plant Product

The SaaS product for Plant Products delivers focused technical support and consumable goods to specialty horticulture industries in Canada and USA. Developed a commercial web application for the world of plants and greenery using .NET Core and Angular. Utilized .NET Core REST API to implement a robust and scalable back-end system, and Angular for the developing user-friendly front-end interface. Implemented features such as an extensive catalog of plants with detailed information and care tips, an online shopping platform for high-quality plants and gardening supplies, and a vibrant community for plant enthusiasts to connect and share their experiences. The application was designed to provide a comprehensive resource for all levels of plant enthusiasts, delivering a seamless and engaging user experience.

Technology Stack : MySQL Database, HTML, SCSS, Angular, .Net Core , BootStrap.

ProweSolution Websit

Developed and implemented a comprehensive website for a hotel using WordPress and various plugins, providing an easy-to-use platform for customers to book rooms, view information about amenities, and access other important details about the hotel. Utilized best practices and latest technologies to ensure the website was visually appealing, user-friendly, and optimized for search engines and performance.

Hotel CrossView Website
